The paper proposes a data mining approach for wind power forecasting, which involves clustering and neural networks. This falls under the domain of machine learning and data mining, which is covered by several arXiv CS sub-categories. Specifically, cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) are the most likely categories as they directly relate to the proposed approach. Additionally, cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.DM (Data Mining) are also possible categories as they cover topics related to clustering and data mining.
